89">semel</ingredient> <ingredient en="parsley" commodity="Q65522500">pettersil</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="common sage" commodity="Q1111359">salua</ingredient> vnd das <ingredient en="spice" commodity="Q42527">gburcz</ingredient> dar vnder</instruction> vnd <instruction>gewß in den <tool en="mortar" commodity="Q45778">morsar</tool> vber dy <ingredient en="chicken" commodity="Q864693">hunr</ingredient></instruction> vnd <instruction>pach es chuell ab das es sich woll durch cziech</instruction> vnd <servingTip>gibs haiß czw essen</servingTip> <closer>etc.</closer></div></body></text></TEI>